Package: SAfeR
Type: Package
Title: Stay SAfer in South Africa
Version: 0.1
Date: 2017-07-03
Author: c(person("Aida","Ylanan",  , "a1daylanan@ucla.edu", person("Jason", "Chong", ,"jasonchongg@gmail.com", person("Paola", "Scaramuzzi", ,"pascar18@gmail.com")))
Maintainer: Aida Ylanan <a1daylanan@ucla.edu>
Description: This package offers a deep insight on South African crime rates between 2005
and 2015. It allows users to obtain information for specific years, geographic areas (provinces
and stations) and types of crime. On top of this, it allows the user to create useful
visualizations of the data.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Imports: dplyr, ggplot2, ggthemes, forcats, tidyr, reshape2
Suggests: testthat
